    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a solid project or a budget-friendly option for someone handy. While the car starts and runs, the exterior shows clear signs of age with some fading paint and various scuffs, and the interior has noticeable wear on the upholstery. Mechanically, it is functional, though it will likely need some routine maintenance and minor repairs in the near future to ensure long-term reliability. It's an honest car that reflects its age and usage, offered at a price that leaves room for the next owner to make improvements.",
