    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended only for those seeking a major project or a parts donor. The exterior shows substantial rust along the frame and wheel wells, along with multiple deep scratches and a cracked windshield. Mechanically, the engine runs roughly and will require significant diagnostic work and repair before it can be considered roadworthy. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with several tears, and the electronics are inconsistent. It is priced to reflect these extensive needs and is sold strictly as-is.",
