    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This vehicle represents the absolute pinnacle of automotive preservation. Meticulously maintained and presented in showroom condition, it offers an unparalleled experience for the most discerning collector. Every aspect of this motorcar, from its flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care rarely encountered in the pre-owned market. This is an exceptional opportunity to acquire a vehicle of peerless integrity and engineering excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
