    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You honestly have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in truly flawless condition. It\u2019s basically brand new\u2014always garage-kept and meticulously cared for. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot, this is the one for you! Feel free to reach out with any questions, I'd love to chat!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
