    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true collector-grade specimen that defines the 'mint' standard. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, retaining its deep, mirror-like factory finish with absolutely no swirl marks or stone chips. Inside, the cabin remains in a showroom state\u2014the premium leather is supple with no bolster wear or creasing, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component and switch functions with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is flawless, having undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection with a comprehensive binder of service records included to verify its history. It features a recent professional-grade ceramic coating and sits on pristine wheels with no curb rash. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to own a time-capsule vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
